edu.fgcu.stesting.uiesg.data

Class MouseActionInputDataImp

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.fgcu.stesting.uiesg.data.MouseActionInputDataImp
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MouseActionInputData

    public class MouseActionInputDataImp
extends java.lang.Object
implements MouseActionInputData
    MouseActionInputData (MAID) is a container for the raw mouse data. Instances will store the locations, timestamps and types of all MouseEvents generated by the browser window.
    Author:
    oalpha
